current-chamber.#text: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

quote.#text:
Corporal Michael J. Crescenz Department of Veterans Affairs
		  Medical Center

official-title.#text:
To designate the medical center of the Department of
		  Veterans Affairs located at 3900 Woodland Avenue in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania,
		  as the

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#text:
Corporal Michael J. Crescenz Act of
			 2013
{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.@value: Corporal Michael J. Crescenz Act of 2013

text.#text: This Act may be cited as the

header.#text:
Corporal Michael J.
			 Crescenz Department of Veterans Affairs Medical Center

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#tail:
located at 3900 Woodland Avenue in Philadelphia,
			 Pennsylvania,
			 shall after the date of the enactment of this Act be known and designated
			 as
			 the

quote.#text:
Corporal Michael J. Crescenz Department of Veterans Affairs Medical
			 Center

text.#text:
Any
			 reference in any law, regulation, map, document, paper, or other record of
			 the
			 United States to the medical center referred to in subsection (a) shall be
			 considered to be a reference to the Corporal Michael J. Crescenz
			 Department of
			 Veterans Affairs Medical Center.

{http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/}title.#text: 113 S229 ES: Corporal Michael J. Crescenz Act of 2013
